---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Robotic Machine Tending — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="Robotic load/unload for CNC mills, lathes, EDM, and injection molds, automated under the Formic Full Service model. The most repetitive, dangerous, and hardest-to-staff jobs on your floor, handled."
  ogTitle="Robotic Machine Tending — Formic"
  ogDescription="Robotic load/unload for CNC, lathes, EDM, and injection molds. Fully supported, flat monthly rate."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/machine-tending" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>Machine Tending
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Machine Tending</div>
    <h1>Robotic Machine Tending.<br><em>Mill, lathe, mold. Hands-Off.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Robotic load/unload for CNC mills, lathes, EDM, and injection molds, automated under the Formic Full Service model. The most repetitive, dangerous, and hardest-to-staff jobs on your floor, handled.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · machine tending</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why It Matters</div>
      <h2>Spindle uptime is <em>everything</em>.</h2>
      <p>In precision manufacturing, a stopped spindle is lost margin. Most shops lose 20–40% of available spindle time to operator-bound load/unload cycles, breaks, and shift changes. Robotic machine tending recovers that time: no additional headcount, no shift coverage required.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Lights-out third shift on equipment you already own</li>
        <li>24/7 support and 100% maintenance — included</li>
        <li>No CapEx — one flat monthly rate, fully supported</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get a quote →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg" alt="Formic robot tending a CNC machine on a precision floor" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">CNC tending · 24/7 spindle</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/MachineTending-CNC.jpg">
        <source src="/ATLAS_EOAT.webm" type="video/webm" />
      </video>
      <span class="img-cap">Vision pick · part presentation</span>
    </div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — How It Works</div>
      <h2>How Robotic <em>Machine Tending</em> Works.</h2>
      <p>Bin or fixture-based part presentation. Vision-guided pick handles orientation. Robot loads, machine cycles, robot unloads. Out-of-spec parts are diverted at the gauge before they leave the cell.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Compatible with Fanuc, Mazak, Haas, DMG Mori, Okuma, and most major CNC and lathe platforms</li>
        <li>Inline gauging integration for in-cell quality verification</li>
        <li>Bin picking from gaylords, totes, or fixtured trays</li>
        <li>Multi-machine tending: one robot, two or three spindles</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Specs</div>
      <h2>Built for <em>your machines</em>.</h2>
      <p>We adapt around your machines, not the other way around. Designed to integrate with the spindles you already run.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Reach: 1.3 – 2.6 m, with track-extended options for multi-machine cells</li>
        <li>Payloads: 5 – 150 kg, EOAT-dependent</li>
        <li>Part weight range: application-dependent, scoped per cell</li>
        <li>Compatible with most major CNC, lathe, EDM, and IMM platforms</li>
        <li>Cycle integration via M-code, Modbus, EtherNet/IP, and OPC UA — compatible with most modern and legacy machine controllers</li>
        <li>Safety: scanners, fenced or collaborative configurations available</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/full-service" class="larr">How Full Service works →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-9787.jpg" alt="Robot loading a precision part into a fixture" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Fixtured load · gauge · unload</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:flex-start">Full Service Automation</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4.4vw,64px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.04;color:var(--white);margin:10px 0 14px">One monthly fee. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Everything included.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>System design and cell engineering</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Robot, EOAT, and fixturing</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Installation and commissioning</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Inline gauging integration</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>24/7 monitoring and support</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>All maintenance and parts</div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:24px 24px;font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(240,245,241,.85)"><span style="color:var(--orange);margin-right:10px">→</span>Performance SLAs</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Recover the spindle hours<br><em>you're already paying for.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
